data.description: Price Improvement!!! $5000 toward closing costs. Welcome home to this well maintained 5 bed 4 bath home with a pool installed in 2020... Located in the highly desirable Alamo Ranch community, this immaculate residence features a spacious and open floor plan, plenty of natural light, plenty of storage, perfect for entertaining guests or simply relaxing. The upstairs boasts a vast primary suite and an oversized loft area perfect for a second living area or game room. The beautifully updated (2021) kitchen is a chef's dream, with stainless steel appliances, stone countertops, and a large island for preparing meals. The roof was redone in 2017 with 30 year shingles. The home is located on a cul-de-sac with a green space behind you. The Alamo Ranch community is ideally situated just minutes away from major highways , offering easy access to shopping, dining, and entertainment options throughout San Antonio. **All room sizes are estimates; please confirm sq ft.
